<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC86A77F81E902D17FEBC3F" pageId="51" pageNumber="809" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC86A77F81E902D17FEBC3F" blockId="51.[2016,2611,1534,1962]" pageId="51" pageNumber="809">
Populations now attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC86A77F677902D1607BD8F" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="51" pageNumber="809" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lanzai">Hypsugo lanzai</taxonomicName>
were previously treated as 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC86A77F68090C517DEBD8F" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[2428,2526,1692,1725]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="51" pageNumber="809" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ariel">H. ariel</taxonomicName>
. Relationship to other 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC86A77F724909A1746BDD6" box="[2264,2374,1731,1764]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="51" pageNumber="809" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hypsugo</taxonomicName>
has not yet been tested on genetic grounds. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
